課程概述 Course Description
       承續細胞生物學(一)，在分子層次探討細胞與細胞間之互動、生殖細胞之結合，個體之發育及細胞之分化。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
使學生具備細胞生物學專業知識建立學生溝通、討論的能力訓練學生邏輯思考的能力 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction of the course (II)2Visualizing cells + Discussion3Visualizing cells + Discussion4Visualizing cells + Discussion5Cell cycle/Cell death + Discussion6Cell cycle/Cell death + Discussion7Cell cycle/Cell death + Discussion8Cell cycle/Cell death + Discussion9Cell junctions & the ECM + Discussion10Cell junctions & the ECM + Discussion11Cell junctions & the ECM + Discussion12Cell junctions & the ECM + Discussion13Mid-term Examination (30%)14Cancer15Development of multicellular organisms 16Stem cells and tissue renewal17Infection & immune system18- 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


